descript.abstract: Cuba Demographic Census Data (Municipality), 2002 is a polygon theme representing Municipalities (2nd level administrative units) in Cuba as of 2002. Attribute data include summary results of the 2002 Cuban census questions regarding demographic characteristics. The documentation of these variables can be found in the "Demographic" section from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Cuba 2002 Census collection.
